These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, rock
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | rock | reggae |
| Birthday     | july    | march   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: berlin, paris
2 different games are played: domino, monopoly
1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | paris | berlin        |
| Game      | domino  | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, june
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid
1. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | june    | march |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, electrician
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports
1. the electrician is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Job   | engineer      | electrician |
| Movie-Genre       | martial-arts | sports    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
