2 different games are played: canasta, snooker
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby           | woodworking | rock-climbing |
| Game   | snooker    | canasta         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, vegafina
City: new-york, berlin
1. the person traveling to new-york is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Cigar       | vegafina | bongani  |
| City   | berlin  | new-york |

